: red;\">避免和印度女人握手</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n9. 當印度人說:「Oh! my friend!」代表背後另有企圖<br />\n10. 一句「Namaste!」走遍印度"},{"pid":"97e1c8f86f5764979c240f97b2e514f8640955f3","tid":511654,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"印度人點會左手用廁紙?<br />\n<br />\n佢地本身就唔用廁紙齋用手指黎抹屎"}]}